on generation through real local modules; assert message contains required fields and the correct prep instructions for each visit type.","plan_consistent":true,"plan_consistent_note":null,"level_probabilities":{"Unit":0.33,"Integration":0.6,"System":0.04,"Agentic":0.02,"Workflow":0.01}},{"behavior_id":10,"description":"End-to-end intake pipeline (validate → insurance → triage → schedule → confirm) completes automatically for a real submission.","minimum_level":"Workflow","justification":"This spans multiple steps and includes at least one real agentic decision in-sequence with external/API and DB interactions. Single-step tests cannot catch cross-step state propagation failures.","test_description":"Execute a full real intake run using a production-like submission through all pipeline stages with real dependencies enabled; assert terminal success, persisted appointment, and sent confirmation without manual intervention.","plan_consistent":true,"plan_consistent_note":null,"level_probabilities":{"Unit":0.01,"Integration":0.03,"System":0.01,"Agentic":0.1,"Workflow":0.85}}]}
